#: ../../../async-programming/combinators-and-composition.md:354
msgid ""
"The [Concurrent Execution](concurrent-execution.md) chapter shows how to run "
"multiple pipelines concurrently using `tokio::spawn`, and the [Scheduling "
"and Streams](scheduling-and-streams.md) chapter explains how the scheduling "
"policy distributes pipelines across CUDA streams."
msgstr ""
